# 2️⃣ Set Interface

A Set does not allow duplicate elements.

---

## HashSet

### Features

* No Duplicates
* Unordered
* Fast Performance

```java id="mk92wb"
HashSet<String> set = new HashSet<>();

set.add("Java");
set.add("Python");
set.add("Java");

System.out.println(set);
```

### Output

```text id="lhl7j8"
[Java, Python]
```

---

## LinkedHashSet

* No Duplicates
* Maintains Insertion Order

```java id="by5wdl"
LinkedHashSet<Integer> set = new LinkedHashSet<>();

set.add(100);
set.add(200);

System.out.println(set);
```

---

## TreeSet

* Sorted Order
* No Duplicates

```java id="m0hzr2"
TreeSet<Integer> set = new TreeSet<>();

set.add(30);
set.add(10);
set.add(20);

System.out.println(set);
```

### Output

```text id="4x1jzc"
[10, 20, 30]
```

